    <!-- /Jumbotron   -->
    <div class="container pt-4">
      <!-- about-->
      <div id="about" class="row">
        <div class="col-lg order-lg-2">
          <h3 class="mb-4">Mural Segments</h3>
          <%= image_tag("bride.jpg", border: 0, style:'width:100%') %>
          <p>Each beautiful segment of the community mural was inspired by a community member. There was extensive community input!</p>
          <p>You can let us know what your favorite segment of the mural is. What does it inspire in you?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg order-lg-1">
          <h3 class="mb-4">About the main Artist</h3>
          <div>
            <%= image_tag("cornelio.jpg", border: 0, style:'width:100%') %>
          </div>
          <p><a href="http://corneliocampos.web.unc.edu">Cornelio Campos</a> is a self-taught Mexican-American artist based in Durham, N.C. </p>
          <p>Vibrant colors, iconic American symbols, and intricate geometric patterns define Mr. Campos’s work. </p>
          <p>Through his paintings, he illustrates some of the harsh realities of immigrating to America that immigrants often overlook. Moreover, he highlights deep-seated political issues that contribute to Mexican immigration</p>

        </div>
         <div class="col-lg order-lg-3">
          <h3 class="mb-4">Other colaborators</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong><a href="https://www.zsr.org"> Z Smith Reynolds Foundation</a></strong>: Funder</li>
            <li><strong><a href="https://elfuturo-nc.org">El Futuro</a></strong>: Grantee and Main organization</li>
            <li><strong><a href="https://scrapexchange.org">The Scrap Exchange</a></strong>: Property Owner</li>
            <li><strong><a href="https://elcentronc.org">El Centro Hispano</a></strong>: Community involvement</li>
            <li><strong>Estephani Sanchez</strong>: Artist Aprentice</li>
            <li><strong>Sandee Washington</strong>: Past artist</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /about -->
      <!--  Segments    -->


      <h1 id="segments" class="display-4 text-center my-5 text-muted"><br>Segments</h1>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
            <img src="/assets/tree.jpg"  class="card-img-top" alt="Tree">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">Tree</h4>
                <p class="card-text">The world Tree of life displays two hands as roots and treebark holding a green world... what does this inspire you?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card mb-3 class="img-thumbnail">
            <img src="/assets/Liberty.jpg"  class="card-img-top" alt="Tree">
            <div class="card-body">
             <h4 class="card-title">Statue of Liberty</h4>
             <p class="card-text">"a universal symbol of freedom. Originally conceived as an emblem of the friendship between the people of France and the U.S. and a sign of their mutual desire for liberty, over the years the Statue has become much more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
              <img src="/assets/hands.jpg"  class="card-img-top" alt="Hands">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">Hands emerging a rainbow</h4>
              <p class="card-text">What an amazing feeling of safety,  and welcoming embrace, teh sun offers to all  visitors.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
            <img src="/assets/Bienvenido.jpg"  class="card-img-top" alt="Bienvenido">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">Bienvenidos</h4>
              <p class="card-text">Spanish  welcoming message: Bienvenidos a casa to the side of the english version: Welcome Home, The sun and the rainbow is there for all!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
            <img src="/assets/mariposa.jpg"  class="card-img-top" alt="Mariposa">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">Butterfly</h4>
              <p class="card-text">Open wings, a buterfly is present in different points in the mural, as a symbol for immigrants, who move in search of a better life.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="card mb-3">
              <img src="/assets/fireworksAll.jpg"  class="card-img-top" alt="Fireworks">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">Fireworks</h4>
              <p class="card-text">As a display of happiness, fireworks are part of the community mural to brign the message of celebration of our diversity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /segments -->

      <!--callout button-->

      <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-lg d-block mx-auto my-5" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#register">Sign in Now!</button>

       <!-- signup form -->
